title: Dare to Art Your Way with Victor Langlois aka FEWOCiOUS
itunes:title: Dare to Art Your Way with Victor Langlois aka FEWOCiOUS
description:
Artist, FEWOCiOUS aka Victor Langlois, brings his infectious energy and palpable authenticity to the podcast this week. Sharing his journey of self-discovery through art with Betty Who, Victor breaks down the vibrant and unfiltered style to which he attributes all his success. Creating everything from dynamic paintings and sculptures to digital art and NFTs, Victor’s work has broken records with the iconic Christie’s Auction House. Gaining him global attention as one of the most popular NFT artists of his generation, Victor is only just getting started.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
